WEBVTT

00:03:59.741 --> 00:04:03.136
She ended up interviewing her aunt,
Troylynn Robertson,

00:04:03.160 --> 00:04:04.310
for an episode.

00:04:05.231 --> 00:04:07.709
(Recording) KW: With everything
that you went through

00:04:07.733 --> 00:04:08.884
with your children,

00:04:08.908 --> 00:04:10.890
what is any advice that you would give me

00:04:10.914 --> 00:04:12.823
if I had any kids?

00:04:13.827 --> 00:04:17.058
(Recording) Troylynn Roberston:
I would tell you when you have them,

00:04:17.082 --> 00:04:20.138
you know the first thing
that will initially come to mind is love

00:04:20.162 --> 00:04:22.134
and protection,

00:04:22.158 --> 00:04:23.654
but I would tell you,

00:04:23.678 --> 00:04:26.766
even much with the protection
to raise them

00:04:26.790 --> 00:04:30.496
with knowledge of the judicial system --